    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- PROJECT OVERVIEW -->
  <section>
    <h2>Project Overview</h2>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        This project explores multiple demographic indicators using U.S. Census data to better understand housing patterns
        and population distribution throughout New York City.
      </p>
      <p>
        GIS-based thematic mapping techniques were used to visualize total housing units, vacant housing units,
        and the distribution of residents under the age of 18 by census tract.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

